Add Custom Columns To The Product Grid On The Category Editor
=============================================================

A simple module by Tim Reynolds @razialx 
----------------------------------------

Installation: 
Unzip into your Magento Root Directory. Clear your cache. 

Results:
You will now have the Product Type and Visibility columns added to 
the grid. 


This module is provided as-is with no guarantees or warranty of any kind. 
Use at your own risk. 

